Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:03.27,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Flowing water has no form.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:05.06,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A blowing wind can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:06.31,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All cases can be freely deduced!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.77,0:00:08.65,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Happy New Year, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:10.90,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And to kick off the new millennium, a two-hour special!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.78,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:14.41,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:16.32,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.80,0:01:59.13,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's the bottom of the ninth, the score's 3-2 with Chunichi leading by a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:02.97,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ace relief pitcher Komatsu is on the mound with 2 outs and runner Oh on second...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:18.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:22.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four shots to the chest. He's as good as dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:28.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saizo Kano, the Phantom Schemer, at the bottom of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The current's strong around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:36.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before he can float to the surface, he'll be fish food.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:40.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But did we have to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.63,0:02:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You kidding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He went chicken after we killed that bank teller!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:47.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was gonna rat us all out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.06,0:02:50.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the cops know our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never mind him, what are we gonna do with the dough?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of the 400 million yen, the cops have the serial numbers for 300 million, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:03:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.45,0:03:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've taken care of the big problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now all we have to do is bide our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:16.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little gift from your old pals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No hard feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it! A record!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:41.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The answer has got to be a record!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:43.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Special announcement?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:54.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:04:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Something important most people in Japan had during the Showa era..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Do you still have it with you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.18,0:04:08.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The first ten people who bring this valuable but increasingly obsolete item..."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.43,0:04:10.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next part! Read the next part!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief, don't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:17.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"...are invited to a free Ogasawara dolphin tour, three days and two nights"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:23.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's try bringing in a record! We can still make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:26.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you'd like to see dolphins, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:30.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have anything to do this long weekend anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. Forget about it! This tour sounds fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And your answer's wrong, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:47.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it was records, they wouldn't have written "people in Japan".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:49.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, what is it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:50.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Samurai spirit", that's what modern Japanese people are lacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.73,0:04:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How are you going to bring something like that down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I've never had samurai spirit, and I doubt I ever will!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:05.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe yo-yos... bell-bottoms...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about kombucha?{this is the English term for koucha kinoko, though kombucha in Japanese is something else. -uso.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.45,0:05:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Designer clothes... Nintendo{Famicom. I took the liberty of using what it was generally referred to here, but you can edit this back if you feel like. -uso.}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know! How about the frill-necked lizard?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a popular pet back in the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:16.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.38,0:05:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The answer... might just be...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:25.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:28.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please board the cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yay! You were right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a lucky guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:40.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad I hung onto those old bills!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and hide it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll give away the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so stingy, Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not something people can get their hands on that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! It's not this? Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, this is real fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:10.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.26,0:06:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a pamphlet for today's tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, what number are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's 3 in your party, so not counting the boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there's 1 more opening on the tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gee... We just made it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.03,0:06:29.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's right, the maximum number for the tour was 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:33.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But this sure is a huge ship for such a small group.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, we're going!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:38.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like a hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be riding this to Ogasawara? Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:46.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:50.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three guests? Are you a family?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you'll have room 110. It's a double.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:07:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Masaru Furukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the organizer of the tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.10,0:07:02.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to thank him for giving me the opportunity to sail on this fantastic ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.15,0:07:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, we haven't met him either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't met him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.32,0:07:13.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He reserved the ship over the phone and told us how to select the passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The charter fee was paid by bank transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm sure he'll be waiting for us at Ogasawara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.67,0:07:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, may I please have your names?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:38.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Kogoro Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A former detective with the Metropolitan Police Department,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and now a famous private eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:51.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,P-Police Superintendent Samezaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.15,0:07:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm nobody's superintendent now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:59.24,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Toji Samezaki (62)\NFormer Superintendent, Homicide Department
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.74,0:07:59.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just an old fogey. Retired two years back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:04.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that you, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're all grown up and pretty as a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what brings you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just wanted to look at the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, today's a special day!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A special day?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess you've forgotten since you quit the force ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, how's your pretty wife doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:32.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not still separated, I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Just forget about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:40.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh...excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No... Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:45.29,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Teruyoshi Kameda (45)\NPassenger
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A seal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.55,0:08:56.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You dropped this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank {\i1}you{\i0} very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.81,0:09:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, y-you're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you thanking him? You picked it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:12.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:17.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What is it? Are you talking to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:21.87,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Korehisa Kanie (46)\NPassenger
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.41,0:09:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:26.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it? Let's go have a drink over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir! Allow me to carry those!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.67,0:09:30.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No thanks, I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.09,0:09:35.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alone, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.67,0:09:36.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:39.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not counting the little boy, he's the tenth person here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.55,0:09:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we can get the ship moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're already behind schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:49.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not yet! There's that old man who came at the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He left to go get something he forgot, but hasn't come back yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He just dropped by to tell me he was going to take a nap until dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:02.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he didn't want to be disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? When did he get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:11.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, we've got ten winners,\Nso please send the rest of the crowd home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! I'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.09,0:10:16.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, sir, you'll be in room 107.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.26,0:10:20.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:24.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't I seen you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No... You must be mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:29.10,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Minoru Ebina (42)\NPassenger
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.52,0:10:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never seen you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:39.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find someone on the wanted list, Superintendent Samezaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.40,0:10:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks to you people, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r},\NI'm certain we'll have a safe journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.20,0:10:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, he's a former police officer\Nand you're a private investigator.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.12,0:10:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's three of you on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:52.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's someone besides us?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.30,0:10:58.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, another detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's not anyone who looks the part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:05.72,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Thank you all for joining us today on the S.S. Symphony.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:07.68,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We are now leaving the dock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:11.19,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We are scheduled to arrive in Ogasawara tomorrow morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.15,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}so relax and have a pleasant journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.26,0:11:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the king of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said she wanted to do that once in her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:51.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's been watching too many movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the ship sinks, that won't be funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:06.57,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Sadao Kujirai (50)\NPassenger
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:02.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The mighty ocean glowing in the sunset...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:06.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With that view in front of you,\NI understand why you'd want to shout.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That felt good!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.54,0:12:12.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sea certainly is wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.66,0:12:15.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is! It helps you forget all your troubles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.54,0:12:21.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes... The sea covers everything for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:25.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your sad memories, your uncertain future...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.92,0:12:26.01,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nagisa Isogai (27)\NPassenger
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even... dead bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.77,0:12:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dead bodies?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry, I shouldn't have said such a horrible thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.98,0:12:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lost my father at sea a long time ago.\NI can't help thinking of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:49.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've all got to thank this Furukawa person for organizing the tour.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know who he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:54.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember that seal I picked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:58.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's when I saw the letters "Furukawa".
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.59,0:13:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw too, right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why you thanked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy from earlier with the seal must be Furukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:17.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he's going to surprise everyone\Nby revealing his identity at dinner tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I overheard his name, and I think it was Kameda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mouri! They're announcing dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:30.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:38.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're the famous Sleeping Kogoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.13,0:13:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What an honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I'm gonna rest up in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still get seasick easily, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I pour you more wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:59.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It feels kind of lonely, our little group\Nwandering around this huge ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.52,0:14:02.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I agree with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.19,0:14:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Including the two people resting in their rooms,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.07,0:14:06.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there are only eleven passengers on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's if you include me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And those two are the detective and the old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.91,0:14:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:17.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I passed the old man in the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a mighty quiet fellow. Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An oceanographer, I've heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:28.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see, his name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saizo Kano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.05,0:14:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saizo Kano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.98,0:14:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What room's he in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Room 101...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where have I heard that name "Saizo Kano" before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Have you forgotten?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:55.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the mastermind behind the 400 million yen robbery we investigated together!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.54,0:14:59.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saizo Kano, the Phantom Schemer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:15:00.21,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Saizo Kano
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have the master key, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:23.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it is him, he may be armed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As soon as you open the door, get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:35.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:39.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's like no one's even been in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.64,0:16:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this is the room?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes! There's no mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll look on the lower deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri, you check the upper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.58,0:16:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got your letter...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he's not in his room, maybe he's on the deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's in the room next door, 102?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the other detective's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he hasn't come out since getting on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.61,0:16:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.53,0:16:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir, may I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, let me do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.00,0:17:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! I know you're in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer me! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess we have no other choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.25,0:17:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you unlock this door too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don'tcha mess with me, punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you guys doin' here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.35,0:17:25.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's what I'd like to ask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.56,0:17:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Phantom Schemer?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:34.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, my pop told me about a guy like that when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:37.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His real name's Saizo Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was the mastermind behind a 400 million yen heist robbery 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His plans were flawless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:51.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The job went off without a hitch, and he had no trouble shaking off the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.84,0:17:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So people called him the Phantom Schemer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a lone wolf who changed gangs for every heist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:02.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He made it a point not to harm anyone while committing his crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.89,0:18:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then during that big robbery 20 years ago, someone got killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.64,0:18:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, he disappeared into thin air.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:15.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that guy was sleeping in the room next to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.49,0:18:18.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but it was empty when we entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Samezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s looking for him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.07,0:18:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.99,0:18:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My pop told me he died a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:31.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought his jacket washed up on a beach, all bloody and full of bullet holes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:32.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.84,0:18:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That jacket was a decoy to fool the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wasn't the kind of guy who'd die that easily, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured he'd be halfway around the world, counting money with his cronies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:52.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Imagine finding him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the statute of limitations for that case ran out five years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so even if we find him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:19:00.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are ya senile, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.15,0:19:01.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The statue of limitations for murder is 15 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.53,0:19:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it's 20 years for a civil case!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If those guys're caught, they're gonna have to return the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. We can't nab Kano on the murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:17.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but his three cronies still have some time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.05,0:19:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we can get Kano to tell us their whereabouts,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we might just get that money back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:28.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, they might all be on this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we'll just call the police once we get to Ogasawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They can't get away while we're at sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.82,0:19:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You fool! There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you today was special?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's the 20th anniversary of that robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At midnight, those crooks will no longer be fugitives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:19:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we've only got two more hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:01.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The statute of limitations will run out for them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? If it isn't Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.97,0:20:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo, long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:08.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were on this ship too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I was sleeping peacefully in my cabin,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when this old guy came banging on my door and woke me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, is Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:21.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, do you have to ask about her?\NShe's got her life, and I got mine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:24.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're not as close as you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:26.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"You two"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.66,0:20:31.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, I just meant you're such a loving family!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get personal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.00,0:20:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Samezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, did you find that Phantom what's-his-name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah. Mouri and I are gonna look around a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:44.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we'll be waiting in the restaurant downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:49.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hang on! We've gotta help them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You want me to wait on my own\Nwhile a dangerous criminal's lurking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.69,0:20:56.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, then! I'll be waiting for you, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:20:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:02.86,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll be waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:08.49,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'll be waiting, dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something wrong, Superintendent?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's start from the top and work down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.80,0:21:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm kind of surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.72,0:21:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never knew you liked dolphins, Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.52,0:21:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rolwins?{slurring}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you answer the ad\Nin the newspaper to get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:41.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:44.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm here 'cause I got a weird letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A weird letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.86,0:21:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Last week I got a letter telling me\Nto come to Ogasawara for a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.91,0:21:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They enclosed 100,000 yen as an advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:21:58.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,100,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But it was really fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the bills were the old design,\Nand there was no return address.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.59,0:22:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It said "Masaru Furukawa".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.47,0:22:10.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Furukawa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:12.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You know the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? That Furukawa person planned this whole tour!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really? I didn't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The letter said I'd be able to get on the ship\Nif I showed one of the bills at the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.44,0:22:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, you were invited on board\Nas a detective, Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.24,0:22:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never accept cash for a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:35.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just came here to return the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.87,0:22:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It kinda raised my curiosity though.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:40.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But talk about a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.04,0:22:42.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe we're all on the same ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:46.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, when I got to Haneda, I tried to call Kudo...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.34,0:22:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, I mean, old man Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.88,0:22:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no one picked up the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.80,0:22:55.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must've called us right after we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.06,0:22:58.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But here we are anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.39,0:23:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like they say, wolves attract wolves,\Nand detectives attract detectives!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.98,0:23:04.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.32,0:23:07.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, are you the other detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.57,0:23:10.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a lot younger than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.20,0:23:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.36,0:23:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, have they found this Saizo Kano person?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... Looks like they're still looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.45,0:23:19.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want to use this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:26.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-T-Thanks, I appreciate it...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem, just ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why don't we all play some poker?\NWe can go to the lounge over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.14,0:23:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good idea, but what about cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.39,0:23:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I brought a deck with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.85,0:23:41.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.27,0:23:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have anything to do, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.40,0:23:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.27,0:23:48.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.98,0:23:52.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where the hell'd that guy disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.57,0:23:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn... Less than an hour left...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.08,0:23:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.99,0:23:59.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.12,0:24:01.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.04,0:24:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not until the very last second...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:07.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm {\i1}going{\i0} to get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.26,0:24:11.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Samezaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.88,0:24:13.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's search one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.97,0:24:17.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's search this ship from top to bottom, Mouri, one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.72,0:24:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.47,0:24:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.98,0:24:22.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Full house!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.94,0:24:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good grief, you won again...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.02,0:24:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.02,0:24:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the next game, whoever has the lowest score will change places with Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.49,0:24:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, do you know what time it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.57,0:24:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it's five minutes to midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.45,0:24:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem awfully worried about the time. Is anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.79,0:24:47.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just an important day for me tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.75,0:24:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, two-pair, aces and nines!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.47,0:24:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the loser...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.55,0:24:56.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.51,0:24:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright now, miss, be gentle with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.98,0:25:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, by "important day", do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.40,0:25:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The day your lover died?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.28,0:25:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That cocktail.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.32,0:25:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a Bloody Mary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.45,0:25:21.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The day you lost your beloved princess, or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.41,0:25:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no... Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.63,0:25:28.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.75,0:25:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you catch him?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.59,0:25:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's nowhere to be found...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.96,0:25:36.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's the old cop?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.97,0:25:39.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's going to keep looking until time runs out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.93,0:25:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like something to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.06,0:25:43.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure... Water, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.68,0:25:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.89,0:25:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm calling it quits soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.81,0:25:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll call it a day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.06,0:25:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.02,0:25:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right then, after we're done, I'll fix the cards and bring them to your room later.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.74,0:25:59.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.32,0:26:00.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How much for my drinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.87,0:26:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lets see... you had two martinis...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.53,0:26:03.20,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'll pay my bill too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.79,0:26:06.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? My wallet...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.21,0:26:08.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this be yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.79,0:26:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.33,0:26:12.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it out in the corridor, so I picked it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.88,0:26:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I didn't take anything out...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.09,0:26:20.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry, I just wanted to check...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.72,0:26:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to bed too, Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.81,0:26:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, just to the bathroom. Let's take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.23,0:26:30.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.30,0:26:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.68,0:27:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I'll never close that old case.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.80,0:27:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Course, I retired from the force two years ago, so I never really had the right...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.02,0:27:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.40,0:27:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I still get a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.61,0:27:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.32,0:27:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.86,0:27:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.49,0:27:28.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did your best, Superintendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.79,0:27:31.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.83,0:27:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, Mouri, let's drink up!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.42,0:27:36.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure! I'm with you all the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.21,0:27:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.67,0:27:42.43,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Gee, that's generous of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.67,0:27:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know the old man was in charge of the case,\Nbut don't you think he's a bit obsessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.77,0:27:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But just like always—
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.73,0:27:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.02,0:27:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was outside... Somewhere on the upper deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.27,0:27:56.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A gunshot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.90,0:27:57.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri! What's the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.98,0:28:00.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,12:08!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.66,0:28:10.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The flag...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.91,0:28:13.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The flag's on fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.00,0:28:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.71,0:28:18.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard a firecracker or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.80,0:28:21.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kudo, do you think this is just some prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.84,0:28:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Look at that, Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.22,0:28:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.14,0:28:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.18,0:28:30.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"My phantom shall rise from the dead with the help of Poseidon"
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.06,0:28:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's somethin' written on this 10,000 yen note!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.89,0:28:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch the knife!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.10,0:28:36.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who're you talking to? I'm no amateur!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.65,0:28:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, go get me a plastic bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.11,0:28:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.32,0:28:44.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you always carry those things around?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.11,0:28:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Old habits die hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.41,0:28:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's written on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.49,0:28:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My phantom shall rise from the dead\Nwith the help of Poseidon."
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.38,0:28:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.79,0:29:01.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-He's alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.17,0:29:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it... He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.80,0:29:05.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.05,0:29:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.35,0:29:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.39,0:29:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Captain! Explosion on the stern!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.23,0:29:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop all engines! Extinguish the flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.23,0:29:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop all engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.07,0:29:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.82,0:29:24.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was an explosion at the stern this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.90,0:29:27.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's on fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.49,0:29:31.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the box the emergency escape ladder is kept in.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.62,0:29:34.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why...would anyone do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.00,0:29:38.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A body!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.50,0:29:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody's being burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.47,0:29:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn. It's burnt to a crisp.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.48,0:29:59.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way we can identify the body\Nor work out the time of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.10,0:30:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This could even be Saizo Kano.\NWe sure can't find him anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.03,0:30:09.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to investigate further.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.24,0:30:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.87,0:30:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,L-Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.24,0:30:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wristwatch he's wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.04,0:30:22.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think that's the gold watch he was wearing when I asked him for the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.63,0:30:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.96,0:30:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's scorched badly, but this sweater does look like his.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.55,0:30:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And these look like his pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.22,0:30:34.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.64,0:30:36.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would anyone do this to Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.56,0:30:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Funny, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.23,0:30:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.11,0:30:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just look at him, looks how he's posed...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.53,0:30:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His upper body and his arm are raised.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.40,0:30:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It almost looks like he's trying\Nto sit up and show us the watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.07,0:30:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.95,0:30:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's heat rigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.79,0:30:57.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Burnt bodies, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.00,0:31:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The skeletal muscles react to the\Nheat and contract with thermocoagulation,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.62,0:31:06.96,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Heat rigor
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.62,0:31:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which causes heat rigor.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.79,0:31:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are more muscles to bend the\Narms and legs than to stretch 'em out.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.96,0:31:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the joints start to bend,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.22,0:31:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the body winds up lookin' like a boxer in the ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.56,0:31:19.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All burnt bodies move into that shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.48,0:31:22.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.27,0:31:25.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move importantly, the problem is the watchband.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.19,0:31:28.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watchband? What's wrong with the watchband?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.61,0:31:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the strap. It's all loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.20,0:31:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean anything.\NSee the can near the victim's feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.66,0:31:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That explosion was probably set off\Nwith the gasoline in this can...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.79,0:31:44.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The explosion was powerful\Nenough to destroy the can.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.33,0:31:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It probably blew the watch loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.84,0:31:48.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're probably right...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.09,0:31:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must've also blown off the\Nvinyl sheet covering the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.97,0:31:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vinyl sheet?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.93,0:31:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. When the Superintendent and I came\Nhere looking for Kano, it was on the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.89,0:32:01.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.35,0:32:06.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then? You did look inside the box, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.82,0:32:10.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. As you can see, the box is\Ntied securely from the outside,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.86,0:32:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I didn't think anyone could hide inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.49,0:32:18.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one could have been in that box then anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.29,0:32:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I got back to the lounge,\NKanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.42,0:32:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.50,0:32:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that smart-aleck kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.05,0:32:29.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name's Heiji Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.63,0:32:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His father's the chief of the Osaka police department.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.38,0:32:38.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, so he's Heizo's kid? No wonder he knows his stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.26,0:32:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know the chief of police?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.77,0:32:45.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure. We used to face off in kendo tournaments.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.10,0:32:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was no match for him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.32,0:32:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hattori.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.94,0:32:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check out this weird stuff on the guy's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.82,0:32:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weird stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.12,0:32:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.20,0:33:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ain't this silicone?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.08,0:33:05.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, polydimethylsiloxane.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.12,0:33:06.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otherwise known as silicone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.25,0:33:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's warped from the heat,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.09,0:33:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but this stuff's used in plastic surgery a lot\Nto heighten the bridge of the nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.63,0:33:15.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means... This stiff changed his face...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.05,0:33:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm pretty sure he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.05,0:33:21.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Er, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.85,0:33:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll cover him with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.02,0:33:28.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he changed his face, that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.44,0:33:34.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. He could have been one\Nof the four members of the gang
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.28,0:33:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that stole the 400 million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.32,0:33:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that body really is Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.20,0:33:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there's a good chance his pal\NKameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was also part of the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.54,0:33:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two buddies with face lifts,\Nmeeting again after all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.75,0:33:52.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet the third member...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.75,0:33:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is that guy sweatin' bullets in the back of the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.13,0:34:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Says his name's Kujirai.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.22,0:34:01.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.89,0:34:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He acted suspicious when he borrowed\Nthat match from Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.35,0:34:09.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another thing's buggin' me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.27,0:34:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy shouted somethin' funny back on the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.73,0:34:14.53,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}H-He's alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.53,0:34:19.70,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew it... He's... alive...!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.03,0:34:24.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was freakin' out over that ¥10,000 bill\Nthat was pinned to the deck with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.41,0:34:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Written on the bill were these words:
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.67,0:34:33.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My phantom shall rise from the dead\Nwith the help of Poseidon."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.84,0:34:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "phantom" must be Saizo Kano,\Nthe Phantom Schemer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.59,0:34:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if he's risin' from the dead, he musta been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.35,0:34:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing he was killed by his\Nthree henchmen from the bank robbery.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.69,0:34:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now an old man shows up,\Nclaiming to be Saizo Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.40,0:34:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.40,0:35:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ain't just talkin' about who this\Nold man who vanished really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.66,0:35:03.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why'd all three guys from the robbery\Nhave to be on the same ship
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.95,0:35:04.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,on the day the statute of limitations was set to run out?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.62,0:35:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then there's that weird newspaper ad.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.25,0:35:13.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I wonder about that Masaru\NFurukawa person who put out that ad.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.59,0:35:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be the real name of one\Nof the three gang members, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.55,0:35:20.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, that guy holds the key to this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.26,0:35:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bet he's got a lot hidden\Nup his sleeve, don'tcha think?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.30,0:35:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.97,0:35:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You don't remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.64,0:35:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we heard you say it on the upper deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.02,0:35:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said, "I knew it, he's alive!"
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.31,0:35:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.77,0:35:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.11,0:35:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, 'fess up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.70,0:35:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were talking about Saizo Kano, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.41,0:35:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know... I don't know anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.33,0:35:52.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.96,0:35:55.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is going nowhere fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.34,0:35:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.88,0:35:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've questioned all the ship's staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.21,0:36:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, how'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.72,0:36:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All their alibis are perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.64,0:36:07.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time of the explosion, excluding us passengers,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.22,0:36:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,all the crew members, including the\Ncaptain, were always working in a group.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.98,0:36:15.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We heard something that sounded like a gunshot,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.52,0:36:20.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the explosion occurred\Njust as we rushed to the upper deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.11,0:36:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fire must have been lit by\Nthe one person who wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.57,0:36:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's Saizo Kano, the only guy who was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.87,0:36:32.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't there someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.21,0:36:33.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.75,0:36:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Kameda man who went back to his room\Nbecause he wasn't feeling well.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.50,0:36:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him since.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.21,0:36:41.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.92,0:36:45.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry down to his room and bring him here!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.72,0:36:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.47,0:36:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'll go with ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.31,0:36:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.76,0:36:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.60,0:36:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.02,0:36:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.48,0:37:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.28,0:37:04.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll see you there then.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.28,0:37:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.82,0:37:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Continue on to Ogasawara!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.62,0:37:10.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't we turning back, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.62,0:37:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, they're sending a helicopter out\Nfirst thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.91,0:37:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our ship is loaded with cargo they need on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.21,0:37:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As soon as they're ready, the coast guard will also send a boat out.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.55,0:37:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until help arrives, those detectives\Nwill have to do their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.88,0:37:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Start engines! Raise speed to 20 knots!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.85,0:37:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Start engines! Start engines!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.94,0:37:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.65,0:37:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.44,0:37:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This could be a problem.\NGo borrow the master key again.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.48,0:37:44.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's not locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.28,0:37:48.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}? I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.58,0:37:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.87,0:37:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He doesn't seem to be in.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.50,0:38:00.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then we'd better tell Samezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.17,0:38:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.55,0:38:06.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where'd you go off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.76,0:38:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}? Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.51,0:38:52.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So? Ya find anythin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.14,0:38:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in the engine room below us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.68,0:39:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cartridge case from a bullet,\Nsome slight traces of blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.40,0:39:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and this mysterious letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.32,0:39:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found a suspicious piece of paper too.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.24,0:39:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was crumpled up and thrown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.53,0:39:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.95,0:39:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know the restroom at the\Nentrance to the restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.95,0:39:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was in the trash can inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.95,0:39:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trash can in the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.00,0:39:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then? What does the letter say?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.42,0:39:24.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'll be waiting for you in the engine room. Masaru Furukawa."
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.21,0:39:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masaru Furukawa again...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.34,0:39:30.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Blood stains and an empty cartridge case...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.43,0:39:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is. One shot to the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.60,0:39:40.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt about it, it's a gunshot wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.56,0:39:45.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet the victim was lured to the engine room by the letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.69,0:39:49.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,shot in the head, then stuffed into the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.36,0:39:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that sounds about right anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.28,0:39:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about that piece of paper you found?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.58,0:39:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was probably written on the\Nsame word processor as your letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.08,0:40:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"See you on the stern. Masaru Furukawa."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.34,0:40:08.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is proof that someone\Nlured that Kujirai guy out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.13,0:40:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you know it was Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.88,0:40:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two of the crew saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.55,0:40:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was standin' out there a little\Nafter midnight, lookin' pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.26,0:40:21.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They heard him shout, "Hey, I'm here!"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.68,0:40:25.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When they tried to talk to him, he got real panicky.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.90,0:40:28.82,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Please don't tell anybody I was here!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.82,0:40:33.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After saying that, he hightailed it\Nback to the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.36,0:40:38.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The crewmen hung around for a while\Nto see if somebody else was gonna appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.70,0:40:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but nobody showed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.25,0:40:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were about to return to duty when they heard that gunshot on the upper deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.13,0:40:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the box on fire yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.42,0:40:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.71,0:40:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we haven't found any kind\Nof incendiary device, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.47,0:41:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the killer fired the gun out on\Nthe deck, and set the flag on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.06,0:41:04.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then while everybody was out on the deck,\Nhe snuck down here and lit the box on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.02,0:41:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's so, Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s behavior makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.32,0:41:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Bet he figgered he coulda been the one burned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.91,0:41:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the only question is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.74,0:41:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,how the killed made it down here so quickly\Nafter firing the gun, with no one seeing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.87,0:41:31.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I got a pretty good idea who the killer is.\NWe'll work out the rest soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.80,0:41:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've figured it out too?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.22,0:41:36.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.43,0:41:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wanna see if we're on the same page?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.44,0:41:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First there's the old man claiming to be Saizo Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.77,0:41:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to you, he got off the ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.15,0:42:00.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but later he was suddenly back on board,\Neven though nobody saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.12,0:42:01.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was set up by the killer as...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.83,0:42:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fake!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.79,0:42:09.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That leaves only two possible culprits.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.83,0:42:12.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. The important clue is...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.92,0:42:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the fact that the corpse's elbows\Nwere right in front of his face,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.38,0:42:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that his knees were completely bent.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.26,0:42:26.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer musta pushed the corpse down and\Nraised the arms up when stuffin' it into the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.98,0:42:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one person who'd need to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.40,0:42:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's just a red herring.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.69,0:42:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real killer is hiding somewhere on the ship, playing dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.74,0:42:40.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.70,0:42:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! This watch is solid proof that—
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.37,0:42:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are {\i1}you{\i0} talking about?\NThat's the killer's trump card...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.00,0:42:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.75,0:42:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we've disagreed on a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.05,0:43:00.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. The last time was when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.43,0:43:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.14,0:43:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's find out whose deduction is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.18,0:43:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we make a contest of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.89,0:43:11.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.06,0:43:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.11,0:43:13.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And fix that watch for me, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.61,0:43:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You want me to get this scorched watch running again?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.40,0:43:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.53,0:43:21.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just askin' ya to put it back where it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.70,0:43:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.24,0:43:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Kameda wasn't in his room?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.37,0:43:31.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.12,0:43:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been looking for him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.71,0:43:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot! People don't just vanish into thin air!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.46,0:43:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move aside! I'll look for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.01,0:43:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, I guess I'd better pick up the search...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.97,0:43:48.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I'd like all of you to stay here a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.89,0:43:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.60,0:43:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just a private eye, and that guy's retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.19,0:43:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What right do you have to keep us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.57,0:44:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.86,0:44:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I'm going to rest in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.83,0:44:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.49,0:44:08.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Me three...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.04,0:44:11.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! It's dangerous out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.75,0:44:13.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.96,0:44:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can take care of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.59,0:44:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.34,0:44:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.72,0:44:29.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's gotta be somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.89,0:44:32.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If my deductions are correct,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.60,0:44:37.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}he's gotta be hiding somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.57,0:44:44.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.70,0:44:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A good place to hide?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.12,0:44:48.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know one, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.28,0:44:53.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someplace that's usually off-limits,\Nor can't normally be seen...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.83,0:44:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez! Quit sneaking off! There's a murderer on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.34,0:45:00.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.55,0:45:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.72,0:45:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't you seen him?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.06,0:45:11.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We were wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.14,0:45:15.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Kudo and I were both wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.40,0:45:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.36,0:45:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ship's route is clear for the next 30 km!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.98,0:45:22.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.99,0:45:25.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Raise speed to 293 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.15,0:45:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,30 knots!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.28,0:45:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speed to 30 knots!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.00,0:45:34.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.29,0:45:38.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who's the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.14,0:45:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, didn't you just hear a strange water noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.64,0:45:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange water noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.81,0:46:01.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably just a bonito jumping.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.00,0:46:23.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know I heard it!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.55,0:46:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strange water sound, like something fell into the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.34,0:46:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, it was just a fish jumping!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.64,0:46:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lots of bonito and flying fish around these parts...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.98,0:46:40.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, have you seen the guy with the Kansai accent?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.90,0:46:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kansai accent?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.77,0:46:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he came here to borrow a flashlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.57,0:46:47.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Flashlight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.40,0:46:54.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That means there's a good chance he went\Nout on the deck to look for something!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.16,0:46:58.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then that water sound was...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.25,0:47:00.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't tell me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.13,0:47:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.96,0:47:04.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No way! Not him, of all people...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.17,0:47:06.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no way he...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.22,0:47:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.80,0:47:13.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.14,0:47:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.89,0:47:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.93,0:47:19.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.06,0:47:20.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.73,0:47:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.32,0:47:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be true... It can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.28,0:47:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.53,0:47:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.58,0:47:40.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.55,0:47:47.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.92,0:47:48.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.17,0:47:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got to be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.34,0:47:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could've fallen overboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.68,0:47:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.60,0:47:56.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.60,0:48:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The waves of the open sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.27,0:48:05.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,devour men whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.36,0:48:09.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd never survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.82,0:48:11.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.24,0:48:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.87,0:48:17.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}'s...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.29,0:48:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Him again?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.20,0:48:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's prolly off somewhere sniffing around for clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.83,0:48:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.96,0:48:28.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'm sure he'll turn up sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.26,0:48:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yoshimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.14,0:48:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.56,0:48:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just...sounded like someone I knew, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.77,0:48:46.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never mind that, what's going on here?\NWhat are you three doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.77,0:48:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were helping her look for something...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.74,0:48:53.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.20,0:48:54.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My pendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.78,0:48:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was getting ready for bed,\NI noticed it was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.58,0:49:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went out to look for it, and these men happened by.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.08,0:49:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They seemed to have time on their hands,\Nso I asked them to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.87,0:49:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three heads are better than one, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.71,0:49:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about this locket with the photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.22,0:49:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it on the bow of the ship.\NThe clasp was undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.14,0:49:20.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is it. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.93,0:49:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I must've dropped it when I was there this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.89,0:49:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Nagisa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, the girl in the photo is you,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.36,0:49:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the man holding you is your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.07,0:49:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.69,0:49:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez. Why didn't you give it back to her earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.16,0:49:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.91,0:49:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know whose it was.\NThere's a hole over the dad's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.91,0:49:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, it could have been\Nsomeone else holding his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.21,0:49:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was going to ask about it at dinner, but I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.88,0:49:55.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry... I shouldn't have mentioned the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.59,0:49:59.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. That photo's over 20 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.35,0:50:02.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all I have left...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.27,0:50:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of my father's mementos.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.85,0:50:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell were you guys thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.27,0:50:13.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a murderer somwehere on board! Don't wander off!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.99,0:50:16.99,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Toji Samezaki (62)\NFormer Superintendent\NHomicide Department
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.99,0:50:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri! Why'd you let them out of the restaurant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.99,0:50:22.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er... They said they were going\Nstraight to their rooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.12,0:50:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! You've got right to order us around!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.46,0:50:29.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I don't want to hang around with the group...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.96,0:50:31.42,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Nagisa Isogai (27)\NPassenger
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.33,0:50:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,or with some hysterical old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.88,0:50:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.88,0:50:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's dangerous to be alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.80,0:50:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd rather lock myself in my room with\Nthese kids so we can play cards all night!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.81,0:50:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.06,0:50:45.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Er, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.31,0:50:49.23,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Sadao Kujirai (50)\NPassenger
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.31,0:50:49.23,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Minoru Ebina (42)\NPassenger
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.81,0:50:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I agree that it's dangerous to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.81,0:50:53.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should probably all stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.94,0:50:58.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you were looking for\NKameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. Did you find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.16,0:51:03.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, he's still missing. Along with Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.91,0:51:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you seen Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.79,0:51:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh geez, Heizo's son's missing too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.04,0:51:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it, what the hell's going on on this ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.88,0:51:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, from now on, I want\Nall of you to stay together!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.88,0:51:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer could be out there\Nsomewhere, or he could be one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.76,0:51:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He could be lying in wait for\None of us to wander off alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.10,0:51:29.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.98,0:51:31.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When we heard the first gunshot,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.73,0:51:34.48,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Samezaki{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} was with us in the restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.48,0:51:36.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} had just come back from the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.15,0:51:40.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just as we got to the upper deck,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.20,0:51:41.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}there was an explosion on the stern,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.36,0:51:44.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}incinerating the box with the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.28,0:51:48.62,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Nobody went missing when we went up on deck,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.62,0:51:54.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}so Ebina{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} and Isogai{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}\Ncouldn't have set the fire either.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.21,0:52:00.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We still haven't identified the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.63,0:52:04.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But the only people who could have\Nlit the fire were Kameda{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}, Kanie{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10},
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.97,0:52:13.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and the old man claiming to be Saizo Kano.\NThey were the only three who weren't with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.36,0:52:17.23,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But something's bugging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.23,0:52:20.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Everyone here's giving off weird vibes.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.99,0:52:26.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even Samezaki{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} keeps\Ngetting worked up over nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.95,0:52:29.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.45,0:52:34.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What happened in that case 20 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.55,0:52:45.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hang on, I'm going to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.72,0:52:52.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn, if Hattori were here, he could\Nask the old man about the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.77,0:52:55.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where's he gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.23,0:53:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.69,0:53:03.70,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Agasa Residence
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.24,0:53:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.03,0:53:05.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 400 million yen robbery from 20 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.78,0:53:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were just watching a special on that case!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.62,0:53:13.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The statute of limitations is about to run out,\Nso last night they did a big program on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.21,0:53:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I taped it because I thought you'd\Nlike to see it when you got back.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.96,0:53:20.30,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Did they say anything about the perpetrators?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.30,0:53:23.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see, I'm sure they did...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.14,0:53:28.97,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They showed photos of the ringleader, Saizo Kano,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.97,0:53:34.69,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but they only had composite sketches\Nof the other three, and no names.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.69,0:53:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did they say anything about Kano being dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.40,0:53:42.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. A jacket with bullet holes and\Nhis blood washed up on a beach,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.99,0:53:46.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so the police concluded that his\Naccomplices killed him after a falling-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.99,0:53:50.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did they know it was Kano's jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.87,0:53:53.91,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They found something in the inside pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.91,0:53:56.83,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Something he always carried with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.83,0:53:59.13,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A picture of him holding his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.00,0:54:02.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.30,0:54:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a sad case.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.76,0:54:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the robbers panicked\Nwhen the burglar alarm went off
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.30,0:54:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and started shooting at random.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.14,0:54:09.22,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and started shooting at random.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.22,0:54:14.89,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A stray bullet happened to hit and kill\Na young bank teller named Samezaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.89,0:54:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who did you say was shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.10,0:54:20.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bank teller. Her name was Yoshimi Samezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.56,0:54:24.07,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Poor thing, she was still so young...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.07,0:54:26.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yoshimi Samezaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.57,0:54:27.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It couldn't be..
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.95,0:54:30.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's too much of a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.12,0:54:35.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why are there so many people\Nconnected to that case here on this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.58,0:54:40.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And who is Masaru Furukawa,\Nthe person who organized this tour?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.50,0:54:45.17,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Masaru Furukawa"
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.21,0:54:45.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who could he be?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.43,0:54:52.97,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}W-What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.97,0:54:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.52,0:54:56.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call me if you think of something!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.64,0:54:58.31,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.73,0:55:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd that sound come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.11,0:55:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stern, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.69,0:55:06.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right then, I'll take the perp from\Nthe left, you go around from the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.82,0:55:07.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.32,0:55:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.43,0:55:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No one's here...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.55,0:55:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's impossible! Look around!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.80,0:55:34.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.22,0:55:37.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Where are you, Hattori?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.52,0:55:41.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why aren't you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.69,0:55:45.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You should've come running\Nas soon as those shots rang out!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.40,0:55:49.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's the matter with you, Hattori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.07,0:55:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.28,0:55:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you suppose he went this way back inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.08,0:55:57.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.71,0:56:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's got to be Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.87,0:56:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's trying to confuse us by firing wildly!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.09,0:56:08.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what for?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.42,0:56:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.22,0:56:15.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He... He's trying to kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.89,0:56:20.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... I d-don't want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.06,0:56:24.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't... want to die yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.52,0:56:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please! You've got to help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.78,0:56:33.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you everything I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.99,0:56:39.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.75,0:56:46.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in Saizo Kano's gang, the one that\Ncommitted the robbery 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.04,0:56:48.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came aboard this ship
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.80,0:56:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because the three of us wanted to\Ncelebrate escaping arrest for 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.97,0:56:57.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the others sent me a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.18,0:57:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said once the ship set sail, we'd be safe until\Nthe statute of limitations ran out at midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.81,0:57:06.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He enclosed an old 10,000 yen bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.48,0:57:08.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we hadn't met in years,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.78,0:57:14.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and we'd all changed our faces and our names, so I didn't even recognize them.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.78,0:57:18.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least, not until Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} spoke to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.45,0:57:22.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said that Kameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was\Nthe other member of the gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.91,0:57:27.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, who's trying to kill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.84,0:57:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well... I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.92,0:57:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lying. It's Saizo Kano,\Nthe guy you betrayed, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.47,0:57:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be him! One of the others\Nshot him to death 20 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.64,0:57:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it's probably one of the others.\NHe wants all the money for himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.36,0:57:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't spent the dough yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.36,0:57:56.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.61,0:57:58.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But something's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.87,0:58:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It just doesn't make sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.74,0:58:03.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.75,0:58:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everybody down!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.12,0:58:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright? Kujirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.67,0:58:11.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where? Where were you shot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.17,0:58:14.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.55,0:58:20.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You've been shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.14,0:58:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn, where'd the shot come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.19,0:58:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid! Keep your head down!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.11,0:58:31.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody's out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.90,0:58:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! At the bow of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.49,0:58:37.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn you! I'm not letting you get away this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.32,0:58:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Superintendent!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.54,0:58:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're cornered!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.50,0:58:50.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Drop your gun and surrender!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.88,0:58:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you hear me, Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.17,0:58:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}are{\i0} Saizo Kano, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.01,0:59:01.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.77,0:59:05.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.56,0:59:09.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.28,0:59:21.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One shot in the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.37,0:59:23.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quick death.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.03,0:59:24.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.37,0:59:25.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The body's still warm,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.50,0:59:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the blood hasn't fully congealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.91,0:59:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are burn marks around the bullet wound, so the gun was pressed to his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.34,0:59:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we heard the gunshot, everyone\Nexcept Kanie was in the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.34,0:59:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only plausible explanation is\Nthat Kanie shot himself in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.18,0:59:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See if this fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.48,0:59:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanie was lurking around the bow of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.60,0:59:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he heard his old crony spill the\Nbeans about the case 20 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.69,1:00:01.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he tried to kill him, but didn't succeed.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.86,1:00:06.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Realizing he was trapped,\Nhe gave up and killed himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.79,1:00:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.12,1:00:12.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.21,1:00:14.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this a little fishy?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.54,1:00:19.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The burnt body we found at the stern was\Nwearing Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s clothes and wristwatch.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.80,1:00:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So who was it, really?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.64,1:00:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably Kameda, the other\Nmember who vanished off the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.85,1:00:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or Saizo Kano.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.39,1:00:35.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whoever it is, Kanie here's the one who killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.11,1:00:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably planned to fake his own death\Nby disguising the body and burning it.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.11,1:00:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The problem is how Kanie was able\Nto hide here without being spotted.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.95,1:00:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.75,1:00:54.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something funny tied behind the man's back!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.13,1:00:57.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.34,1:00:58.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A rope ladder!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.80,1:01:04.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a great place to hide when you're playing hide and seek!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.93,1:01:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. Kanie hid from us by hanging from this ladder.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.10,1:01:16.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are rope marks on the arms\Nand legs. Looks like you're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.90,1:01:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.23,1:01:24.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why'd he go to the trouble of faking\Nhis death and then hide out here?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.70,1:01:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.87,1:01:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He planned to appear before someone he wanted to kill,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.91,1:01:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to make them freeze in fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.33,1:01:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.87,1:01:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But who was Kanie trying to kill, that he\Nhad to go through so much trouble?!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:39.09,1:01:42.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kujirai, who just got shot, was one\Nof his old buddies, wasn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.72,1:01:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.60,1:01:54.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're losing a lot of blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.56,1:01:59.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bullet must've nicked an artery.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.11,1:02:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He needs medical attention right away.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.53,1:02:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s just gone to get the first-aid kit.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.65,1:02:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're pretty lucky.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.16,1:02:14.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just damaged your suit and your arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.12,1:02:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mouri! I found it!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.12,1:02:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's the bullet hole.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.79,1:02:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like Kanie definitely fired\Nfrom the bow through this window.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:24.67,1:02:29.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now...all we have to do is find the bullet,\Nwhich is embedded here somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.89,1:02:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.18,1:02:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this what you're looking for?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.35,1:02:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, no doubt about it, this is it!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.10,1:02:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quite a marksman.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.11,1:02:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He barely grazed his target,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.19,1:02:46.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he shot a handgun from quite a distance.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.28,1:02:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.82,1:02:53.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the men in Kano's gang was\Nsupposed to be an expert with firearms!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.58,1:02:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.08,1:02:59.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We got as far as finding out that he might've been in some country's foreign legion,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.67,1:03:01.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but that was about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.75,1:03:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that must've been Kanie.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.80,1:03:07.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.34,1:03:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you brought the first-aid kit.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.14,1:03:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got to stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.56,1:03:19.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.06,1:03:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Isn't he around?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.73,1:03:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy with the Kansai accent?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.94,1:03:29.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came to borrow a flashlight, but never came back.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.91,1:03:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hasn't come to the bridge either.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.16,1:03:35.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange. Where's he gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.62,1:03:39.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, could you look inside everybody's rooms?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.58,1:03:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, but I don't think you'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.83,1:03:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. When we were looking for\Nthat Kameda person with Samezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.55,1:03:49.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,we searched all the rooms then.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.76,1:03:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find any signs of his room being searched?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.68,1:03:55.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's a detective.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.10,1:03:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.98,1:04:02.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aside from Kameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room,\Nevery room was locked.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.31,1:04:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, there is\None room we didn't search!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.44,1:04:08.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, the neat freak...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.99,1:04:12.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Ebina{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room, the guy with the glasses.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.41,1:04:15.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All we found was a suitcase in the middle of his room.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.12,1:04:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There wasn't so much as a wrinkle on the bedsheets.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.49,1:04:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was like he hadn't even unpacked, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.25,1:04:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.42,1:04:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Could you show me that room?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.59,1:04:28.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something Uncle Mouri wanted me to check!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.80,1:04:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.97,1:04:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.48,1:04:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, little boy, did Detective Mouri really ask you to do this?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.36,1:04:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bet! He also said to keep it a secret!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.15,1:04:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go back in. That body's giving me the creeps.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.07,1:04:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... You're right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.24,1:04:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You hurry back too, little boy!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.62,1:05:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.45,1:05:06.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if the killer's offed himself now,\Nthis trip sure has been a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.63,1:05:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet Furukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, whoever he is,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.84,1:05:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,can't wait for our ship to get to Ogasawara...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.63,1:05:16.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Masaru Furukawa...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.30,1:05:19.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The man who planned this tour...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.64,1:05:22.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All the mysteries start here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.60,1:05:28.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If the killer was Kanie{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}, and this\NMasaru Furukawa was Kanie{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} all along,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.57,1:05:32.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}this case almost makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.03,1:05:34.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I still can't explain...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.32,1:05:37.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}the watch the corpse was wearing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.91,1:05:43.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And there's that "Furukawa" seal\Nthat Kameda{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} had.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.75,1:05:49.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it. If only I could figure out\Nwho this Masaru Furukawa is...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.09,1:05:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.35,1:06:02.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you seen a boy with glasses?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.18,1:06:05.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.44,1:06:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masaru Furukawa is...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.40,1:06:15.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A scorch mark?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.99,1:06:20.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And some paint has chipped off, too...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.08,1:06:22.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.00,1:06:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:40.89,1:06:42.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Another one!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.48,1:06:52.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And here!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.32,1:06:54.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I get it!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.78,1:06:58.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's how the killer controlled the time and everyone's movements!
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.53,1:07:01.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And that's why he hired Hattori as a detective!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.87,1:07:03.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why Hattori?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.66,1:07:07.54,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm sure he's famous in the Kansai region, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.91,1:07:11.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why hire a private detective all the way from Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.42,1:07:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, do you know how much you make me\Nworry when you keep going off by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.09,1:07:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I was just about to go back. T-That's why I...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.22,1:07:26.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.48,1:07:31.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.00,1:07:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, you know what a scaredy-cat I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.54,1:07:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're not around, I'll have to\Nsearch this creepy ship all by myself!
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.21,1:08:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.63,1:08:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where'd you get this tennis ball?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.01,1:08:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it under the table while I was\Nlooking for you in the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.19,1:08:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked around, but no one knows who it belongs to.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.81,1:08:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Mr. Samezaki say something when he saw it?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.69,1:08:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.40,1:08:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him since he went up to the bow with Dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.53,1:08:24.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I heard them shouting.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.95,1:08:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like they found an old\Nbullet wound on Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.41,1:08:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what did everybody do the first time
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.54,1:08:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Mouri and the others left the restaurant\Nthe first time to look for this Kano person?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.76,1:08:40.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They all left, one by one.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.76,1:08:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the time I got back to the restaurant with\Nyou and Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, they'd all come back.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.68,1:08:49.60,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.60,1:08:51.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've figured it all out.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.39,1:08:55.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The truth behind this bizarre case!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.37,1:09:08.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've figured it all out.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.03,1:09:10.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All I need now is the proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.20,1:09:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.08,1:09:14.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're looking for a guy with a Kansai accent.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.50,1:09:17.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kid asked us the same thing earlier.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.17,1:09:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've been looking for him too,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.55,1:09:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but so far, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.05,1:09:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.55,1:09:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.63,1:09:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll call back later.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.30,1:09:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.05,1:09:31.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, we'll get the entire crew to search the ship again.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.35,1:09:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.40,1:09:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh... What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.98,1:09:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.98,1:09:43.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.07,1:09:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.15,1:09:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.28,1:09:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, of course!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.03,1:09:51.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.49,1:09:55.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably swimming with the fishies somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.63,1:09:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.21,1:10:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could this mean that...
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.96,1:10:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yup. I think—
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.80,1:10:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.31,1:10:16.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.73,1:10:17.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.31,1:10:19.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.44,1:10:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.40,1:10:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! I want you to get everybody out here!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.40,1:10:27.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've solved the case.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.36,1:10:29.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.57,1:10:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.83,1:10:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true? You've solved the case?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.63,1:10:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I've figured everything out.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.88,1:10:44.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the facts of this case.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.63,1:10:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not going to just tell us\Nthat Kanie was the perp, are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.80,1:10:52.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. The killer {\i1}is{\i0} Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.26,1:10:57.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you said, Superintendent,\Nhe faked his death and went into hiding,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.14,1:10:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,looking for an opportunity to kill...
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.10,1:11:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.48,1:11:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then who was the burned corpse?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.53,1:11:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was Kameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.66,1:11:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} lured Kameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} out and shot him.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.12,1:11:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he put him in the emergency ladder box,\Nand went back to join the others.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:21.38,1:11:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he set the flag on the upper deck on fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.84,1:11:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then when everyone ran up to\Nthe deck, he set fire to the box.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.18,1:11:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason why he didn't dress Kameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nas soon as he was put in the box
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.18,1:11:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was because he was waiting for the superintendent\Nto give up looking for the old man named Kano.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.06,1:11:42.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It takes a long time to dress someone,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:42.69,1:11:45.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he couldn't risk being seen by the superintendent.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.03,1:11:51.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The proof is the way the victim's\Narms were up beside his face!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.70,1:11:54.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you raise the arms when\Nputting the body into the box,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.41,1:11:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's still easy to dress the body\Neven after rigor mortis sets in.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:59.66,1:12:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The strap of the watch was loose,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.29,1:12:06.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,probably because it didn't fit Kameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s wrist.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.80,1:12:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just before lighting the box on fire,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.72,1:12:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} called Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} out to the stern,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.01,1:12:15.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,hoping to pin the crime on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.39,1:12:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, the person closest to the scene\Nof the crime is usually the first suspect.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.94,1:12:22.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.27,1:12:25.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did he have to fake his own death?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.32,1:12:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To frighten his next target, Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.36,1:12:37.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who wouldn't be terrified by the sudden appearance of the man he betrayed 20 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.62,1:12:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Betrayed?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.04,1:12:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. The old man claiming to be Kano was another illusion created to cause fear.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.54,1:12:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the scar on Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.80,1:12:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That old bullet wound proves everything!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.35,1:12:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.97,1:13:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.52,1:13:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was the man thought to have been killed 20 years ago, the Phantom Schemer...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.81,1:13:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saizo Kano himself!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.28,1:13:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lying...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.03,1:13:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.87,1:13:17.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true at all!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.70,1:13:21.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not true...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.95,1:13:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This man couldn't possibly be Saizo Kano...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.46,1:13:27.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Kano is...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.50,1:13:29.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kano is...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.05,1:13:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.84,1:13:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Your father?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.51,1:13:40.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.18,1:13:45.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saizo Kano, the Phantom Schemer, is my real father.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.52,1:13:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I joined this tour to look for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.02,1:13:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was rumored that he was killed 20 years ago by his accomplices,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.40,1:13:58.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I thought that maybe he was still alive...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:59.03,1:14:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't find him on board.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.29,1:14:05.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably had plastic surgery and changed his identity.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.92,1:14:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.67,1:14:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if his features changed,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.63,1:14:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd never mistake my father for another man!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.21,1:14:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he would have shown some sign that he recognized me too...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.55,1:14:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though it's been 20 years since we saw each other...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.60,1:14:24.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what I wanted to hear.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.52,1:14:27.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry to deceive you, Nagisa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.65,1:14:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suspected as much, but I wanted to make sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.82,1:14:35.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I could upset the killer's plan.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.11,1:14:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plan?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.45,1:14:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.82,1:14:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer make it look like Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} killed Kameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.04,1:14:45.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,dressed him in his clothes and set him on fire.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.71,1:14:48.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This would make us think he faked his death.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.46,1:14:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He created the illusion that he was firing a gun around the ship to distract us.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.25,1:14:57.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, he made us think that Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} committed suicide
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.55,1:15:02.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,after shooting Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, one of the other members of his old gang.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.72,1:15:07.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted it to look like Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was actually Saizo Kano,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.77,1:15:14.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and that this murder on the ocean was revenge for the gang's betrayal 20 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.03,1:15:18.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then... you mean... the killer is...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.70,1:15:21.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right. It's someone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.45,1:15:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he's right here!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.78,1:15:25.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.95,1:15:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now! What are you talking about, Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.83,1:15:32.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know the facts!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.29,1:15:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time of that explosion at the stern,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.88,1:15:39.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,all the passengers were on the upper deck!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.84,1:15:42.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And everyone on the crew has an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.93,1:15:47.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You even said there'd have to be some kind of automatic incendiary device.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:47.60,1:15:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.35,1:15:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found the incendiary device.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:51.40,1:15:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found it? In there?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.40,1:15:54.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used a cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.53,1:15:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit poured gasoline into the box with the body,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.03,1:16:02.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then placed a lit cigarette under the lid of the box,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.37,1:16:04.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and tied it in place with string.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.62,1:16:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In about ten minutes, the string burned through,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.58,1:16:11.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,making the cigarette fall into\Nthe box and light the gasoline.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.04,1:16:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.21,1:16:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do you explain the four gunshots we heard at the stern,
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.30,1:16:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then two more at the bow?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.13,1:16:24.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the passengers were around back then too.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.89,1:16:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another cigarette.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.06,1:16:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suspect the killer stuck a lit cigarette and\Na firecracker together onto the handrail.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.11,1:16:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the firecracker exploded,\Nthe evidence fell into the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.44,1:16:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As proof, there are scorch marks\Nand chipped paint on the handrails!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.58,1:16:51.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same trick was used for the gunshots\Nwe heard before we found the burning flag.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.87,1:16:56.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit soaked the flag in gasoline\Nand left a lit cigarette nearby.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.46,1:17:03.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a trick anyone could've pulled off\Nwith just a pack of cigarettes.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.22,1:17:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then who is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.81,1:17:09.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's the real killer?!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.27,1:17:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's...
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.68,1:17:13.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.91,1:17:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.62,1:17:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was an explosion in the rear!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.37,1:17:29.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop all engines! All stations check for damage!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.83,1:17:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.21,1:17:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lower deck! Any damage?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.88,1:17:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No damage!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.76,1:17:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.26,1:17:48.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bomb just exploded about 100 meters behind the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.22,1:17:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,100 meters?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.64,1:17:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that a bomb?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.23,1:17:55.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to be on the safe side,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.90,1:17:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I put it on a life raft,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.40,1:18:00.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and had the raft tied with a rope to the handrail on the stern
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.36,1:18:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so it'd drift away from the ship.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.11,1:18:04.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ebina{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.03,1:18:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the end of the bomb in your suitcase!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.70,1:18:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suitcase?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.62,1:18:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-How did you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.08,1:18:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A tidy room without even a wrinkle on the bed,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.75,1:18:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a suitcase that hadn't been opened,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.17,1:18:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and your constant fretting over the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.84,1:18:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.80,1:18:34.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably prepared the bomb a while ago to kill\Nthe gang responsible for the robbery 20 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.23,1:18:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and avenge the death of your old colleague.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.73,1:18:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Colleague?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.03,1:18:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He counted bills with the technique of a bank teller.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.03,1:18:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I heard him mutter the name\Nof the teller who was killed in the robbery.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.45,1:18:57.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoshimi Samezaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s name...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.63,1:19:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wasn't just my co-worker.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.04,1:19:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was... She was the most important thing in the world to me...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.47,1:19:09.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mean you're...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.84,1:19:12.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the guy who broke down\Nin tears at my daughter's funeral...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.60,1:19:14.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.60,1:19:17.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the funeral, I quit the bank,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.52,1:19:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and drifted from job to job ever since,\Nlooking for the killers,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.40,1:19:24.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,even after the statute of limitations for her murder ran out!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.69,1:19:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see... So it was you...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.11,1:19:32.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the special person Yoshimi asked me to meet...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.12,1:19:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If... If only...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.50,1:19:42.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd come to the bank on time as you promised...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.17,1:19:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She... She wouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.05,1:19:50.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.30,1:19:54.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of my officers was stabbed that day,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.10,1:19:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I was at the hospital when I got the news.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.15,1:20:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You also saw that ad in the paper and joined the tour.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.61,1:20:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...I thought this might be it...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.61,1:20:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If my hunch was wrong, I figured I'd just toss the trunk into the sea before the bomb went off...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.08,1:20:21.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was you!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.04,1:20:26.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the killer who's been picking off the gang members!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.00,1:20:29.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No! It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.13,1:20:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All I brought on board was the bomb!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.72,1:20:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know anything about any guns!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.51,1:20:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true! You have to believe me!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.81,1:20:39.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.14,1:20:42.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know you're not the killer.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.77,1:20:47.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I said before, to make it seem\Nlike Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was the killer,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.73,1:20:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the real killer set up this whole scenario\Nto look like Saizo Kano's revenge.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.83,1:20:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He disguised himself as an old man to board the ship,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.08,1:21:00.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,left to remove the disguise, then boarded as himself,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.75,1:21:05.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to make us think Saizo Kano was on board.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:05.08,1:21:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He left that bill with the mysterious message pointing to Kano on the deck.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.55,1:21:16.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was all to make us think it was Kano trying to terrorize the people who betrayed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.22,1:21:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the bullet wound on Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.60,1:21:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was used to make us think he was Kano,\Nshot by his gang 20 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.98,1:21:30.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what is that wound?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.28,1:21:35.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably a souvenir from his time in the military.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.74,1:21:39.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We believed the gang included\Nan ex-soldier, remember?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.66,1:21:43.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he was one of the accomplices...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.25,1:21:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means...!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.12,1:21:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.46,1:21:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only person who could have come up with a plan like this
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.42,1:21:54.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was somebody who already knew there was\Nan old bullet wound on Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.17,1:21:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mean...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.05,1:21:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you were a member of the gang!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.26,1:22:00.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only you could have done it!
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.43,1:22:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-That's insane!{KEEP! -uso.}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.56,1:22:09.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You waited for Kameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to leave the restaurant after getting your note,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.86,1:22:11.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then you mentioned Saizo Kano's name to us.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.82,1:22:14.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the excitement, you went down to the engine room,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.32,1:22:17.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where you had told Kameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to wait, and shot him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.07,1:22:21.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you hid his body in the box at the stern.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.58,1:22:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The engine room?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.00,1:22:26.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I've already found blood stains, an empty shell casing,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.83,1:22:30.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and the letter he used to lure Kameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} into the engine's room.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.00,1:22:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must've slipped the note\Nunder the door and into the room.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.92,1:22:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} came back to the restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:37.84,1:22:41.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,waited for the superintendent to give up the search for Kano,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.68,1:22:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then left to meet with Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.60,1:22:47.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They probably met in the restroom next door.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.94,1:22:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he knocked Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} out with a drug,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.15,1:22:55.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,stole his clothes and wristwatch,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.03,1:23:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,dressed Kameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body\Nand set up the cigarette device.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:00.03,1:23:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He raised his voice, attracting the staff's attention,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.37,1:23:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he'd have witnesses to attest\Nthat the box wasn't on fire yet,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.58,1:23:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and so he could claim he'd just been called to that spot.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.50,1:23:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He left the note in the restroom trash can,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.92,1:23:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,pretending to be afraid after hearing Kano's name
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.30,1:23:23.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so that Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} would approach him.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.97,1:23:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must've intended to claim that\Nthe note was hidden in the matchbook.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.98,1:23:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He lured you out to make us believe\Nthat Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was the mastermind.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.78,1:23:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He created the cigarette setup with the flag
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.86,1:23:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,before he changed the clothes on the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.62,1:23:50.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That way, when we heard the explosion,\Nhe could run up with everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.29,1:23:53.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We would be his alibi.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.92,1:24:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He moved the sleeping Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nfrom the restroom to the bow
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.43,1:24:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,while we were all focused on\Nthe burning body at the stern.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.22,1:24:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he watched our movements,\Nand after some time had passed,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.14,1:24:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he placed another device at the stern.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.10,1:24:14.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After hearing the sound, while we went running,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.40,1:24:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he went back to the bow,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.03,1:24:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,pulled Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} up, shot him,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.90,1:24:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then shot himself in the arm,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.53,1:24:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,letting the bullet pass through the window into the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.45,1:24:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he set two more of his cigarettes, and was good to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.21,1:24:38.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He just had to gather everyone together on\Nthe stern, claiming to make a confession,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.05,1:24:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and wait for the firecracker to pop.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.26,1:24:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By falling down at the same time as the noise,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.30,1:24:47.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he made it look like he'd been shot\Nby someone standing at the bow!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.72,1:24:51.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a second, Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.14,1:24:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was with him and took a look at his wound right after he fell!
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.15,1:24:58.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he'd shot himself earlier, there'd be more blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.40,1:24:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He used a tennis ball!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.19,1:25:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By holding a tennis ball tightly under his arm,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.95,1:25:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he put pressure on his artery,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.41,1:25:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and stopped the blood flow!
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.66,1:25:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the firecracker went off, he dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.87,1:25:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran found the ball under the table in the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.88,1:25:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must've thrown it away while everyone\Nwas distracted by the second explosion.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.34,1:25:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why didn't he kill Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} when\Nhe dragged him down to the bow?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.59,1:25:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because the trick would seem fishy\Nif Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} appeared to commit suicide
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.68,1:25:33.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,right after the first body was found.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.35,1:25:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wanted us to believe that Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had dressed the body.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.32,1:25:40.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The raised arms of the body and the loose watch strap
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.28,1:25:44.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,were red herrings used to create the illusion.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.95,1:25:49.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's also why he hired Heiji Hattori,\Na private detective from Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.99,1:25:55.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we showed up, Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Ndecided to use us as his patsies instead.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.92,1:26:00.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You got a detective from Osaka\Nbecause you live in the area, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.34,1:26:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,People from Kanto don't say "fix" when talking\Nabout putting playing cards back in a case.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.80,1:26:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great... If you just had some proof.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.60,1:26:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll probably find it when you check the area around the shattered glass.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.94,1:26:22.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll get a luminol reaction.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:22.86,1:26:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There'll be just a trace but you'll find some smears from when he wiped
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.11,1:26:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the blood that splattered when he shot himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.03,1:26:32.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.45,1:26:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a setup! Somebody's trying to set me up!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.54,1:26:38.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.38,1:26:40.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.75,1:26:44.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stars...are so beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.72,1:26:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.18,1:26:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.84,1:26:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A strange star approaching from portside!
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.64,1:26:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.52,1:26:59.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.77,1:27:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.32,1:27:09.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.62,1:27:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can testify that you attacked him\Nand threw him overboard
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.75,1:27:17.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when he found Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} hanging from the bow!
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.21,1:27:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't talk your way out of this one, can you, Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.09,1:27:30.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how did you know Kanie wasn't the killer?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.01,1:27:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.89,1:27:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the moment I noticed that the corpse was wearing a right-handed watch on its left hand,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.19,1:27:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I took Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} off my list of suspects.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.98,1:27:43.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You tried to make him look like you,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.15,1:27:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but you were made a big mistake\Nby putting the watch on wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.99,1:27:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Laid low by your buddy's fancy watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.45,1:27:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is the one\Nwho put the ad in the paper.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.50,1:27:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,20 years ago, he must have promised the other members
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.96,1:28:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that he'd contact them under the name "Masaru Furukawa"
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.33,1:28:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,on the day their statute of limitations expired.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.63,1:28:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The three members gathered here\Nto get their hands on the money.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:10.05,1:28:13.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They couldn't spend it for 20 years,\Nso they left it in a safe-deposit box.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.97,1:28:17.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Back then, to get into such a box in a Japanese bank,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.39,1:28:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you needed a key, a signature and a seal.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.06,1:28:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They split the three among themselves,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.69,1:28:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so that when they had changed their faces, they\Ncould use them as a sign when they met in 20 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.03,1:28:32.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kujirai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was in charge of the signature.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.61,1:28:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When he saw Kameda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and Kanie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nflashing the seal and the key around,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.99,1:28:39.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he identified them as his former partners,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.08,1:28:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and put his plan into action.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.21,1:28:44.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.42,1:28:47.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was going to kill them, steal the key and seal,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.21,1:28:49.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and keep all the money for himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.97,1:28:51.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.55,1:28:56.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just when your statute of limitation expired,\Nyou had to pull off another murder.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.64,1:28:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to win...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.89,1:29:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Against Saizo Kano, and his perfect plans.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.23,1:29:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanted to beat the Phantom Schemer,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.07,1:29:13.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who used to tell me my plans were a joke!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.32,1:29:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.82,1:29:19.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are there so many people\Nconnected to the case on board?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.70,1:29:22.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never said anything about Kano in the ad...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.91,1:29:26.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you know the significance\Nof "Masaru Furukawa"?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.34,1:29:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kano had us use that name all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.67,1:29:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said there were just a few strokes,\Nso it was easy to remember.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.26,1:29:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were to use it when we\Nneeded to contact each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.68,1:29:36.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't think it meant anything...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:38.22,1:29:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.51,1:29:42.02,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Masaru Furukawa"
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.48,1:29:46.69,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Saizo Kano"
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.18,1:29:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Turn "Masaru Furukawa" sideways!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.48,1:29:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kanji spell "Saizo Kano"!
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.48,1:29:50.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I came.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:50.53,1:29:53.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad's name appearing on the day the statute of limitations ran out...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.07,1:29:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't sure, but I had a hunch...
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.95,1:30:00.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Masaru Furukawa" was Kano's alias!\NHe created it with wordplay!
Dialogue: 0,1:30:00.66,1:30:02.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No... It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.33,1:30:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were no match for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.29,1:30:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For the last 20 years,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.80,1:30:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you've always been in Kano's clutches.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.69,1:31:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You fell into the sea?!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.48,1:31:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:52.48,1:31:53.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not kiddin'!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.82,1:31:55.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The guy clocked me from behind and knocked me in!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.94,1:31:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't ya miss me? You're cold!
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.91,1:32:02.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.62,1:32:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to tread water 'til those fishermen saved me.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:07.25,1:32:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had a heck of a time, ya know.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.46,1:32:11.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to take all my clothes off,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.25,1:32:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then tried to signal the ship with a flashlight...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.46,1:32:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe ya didn't notice!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.75,1:32:17.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You... took your clothes off?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.88,1:32:22.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'Course! Wet clothes're heavy\N'cause they soak up so much water!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.51,1:32:25.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I hadn't shed the extra weight, I'd be on the bottom of the sea right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:25.35,1:32:27.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only thing I kept on was my pants,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.93,1:32:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and this. Found it in my pocket.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.90,1:32:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This good-luck charm...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.94,1:32:40.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who knows if this thing actually helped?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.41,1:32:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What're you staring at me for?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.62,1:32:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.29,1:32:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were looking at Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s good-luck charm gave you all dreamy-eyed...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.00,1:32:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.17,1:32:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just wonderin' if I should throw this unlucky thing away!
Dialogue: 0,1:32:56.21,1:33:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm only keepin' it 'cause I don't wanna get cursed or nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.13,1:33:03.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then you shouldn't have forgotten it...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.69,1:33:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three people turned themselves in,\Nsaying they committed the murder?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:20.44,1:33:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Accomplices?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.82,1:33:26.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's only one victim, but there are\Nthree people saying they killed him.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:26.74,1:33:28.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.74,1:33:34.79,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.79,1:33:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: A head as hard as rock
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.80,1:33:41.42,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The next case is super-unique!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.42,1:33:42.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You burned the {\i1}mochi{\i0}, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.97,1:33:43.68,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.68,1:33:44.93,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Look forward to this year too!
